---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about Wessex Whisky Club's mission to bring exceptional whisky experiences while supporting local charities">
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-orange-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
        About Wessex Whisky Club
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-700">
        Where exceptional whisky meets exceptional causes
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700">
            <p>
              Founded in 2018, Wessex Whisky Club began with a simple but powerful idea: 
              combine our passion for exceptional whisky with our commitment to supporting 
              local communities across the South West.
            </p>
            <p>
              What started as informal tastings among friends has grown into one of the region's 
              premier whisky societies, known for our exclusive events, expert-led experiences, 
              and unwavering dedication to charitable causes.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every tasting we organize serves a dual purpose - to educate and delight our 
              members while raising vital funds for carefully selected local charities. 
              To date, we've raised over £50,000 for causes close to our hearts.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500">
              <span>Founder Photo Placeholder</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Values -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Our Mission & Values</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            We curate only the finest whisky experiences, working directly with renowned 
            distilleries to bring you exceptional spirits and expert knowledge.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Every event supports local charities, ensuring that your passion for whisky 
            creates positive impact in our South West communities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Education</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            We believe great whisky deserves understanding. Our events combine 
            tasting with learning, guided by industry experts and distillery representatives.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Meet the Team</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">The passionate individuals behind Wessex Whisky Club</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Team Member 1 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-slate-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-slate-500">Photo</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">James Mitchell</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-medium mb-3">Founder & President</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            A certified sommelier with over 15 years in the spirits industry, James founded 
            the club to share his passion for whisky while supporting local causes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 2 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-slate-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-slate-500">Photo</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Sarah Thompson</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-medium mb-3">Events Director</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Sarah coordinates our charity partnerships and ensures every event runs smoothly. 
            Her background in event management brings professionalism to every gathering.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 3 -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-slate-200 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-slate-500">Photo</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Robert Davies</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-600 font-medium mb-3">Education Coordinator</p>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
            Rob brings technical expertise to our tastings, helping members understand 
            the science and craft behind every dram. He holds multiple whisky certifications.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Statistics Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-amber-600">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center text-white">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">150+</div>
          <div class="text-amber-100">Members</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">75+</div>
          <div class="text-amber-100">Events Hosted</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">£50K+</div>
          <div class="text-amber-100">Raised for Charity</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">25+</div>
          <div class="text-amber-100">Distilleries Featured</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">The South West</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-slate-700">
            <p>
              Based in the heart of the South West, we're proud to serve whisky enthusiasts 
              across Devon, Dorset, Somerset, and Cornwall. Our events take place in 
              carefully selected venues that complement the whisky experience.
            </p>
            <p>
              From historic coaching inns to luxury hotels, we choose locations that 
              enhance the atmosphere and provide the perfect setting for learning, 
              tasting, and connecting with fellow enthusiasts.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our mobile approach means we bring exceptional whisky experiences directly 
              to communities throughout the region, making premium tastings accessible 
              to everyone.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-w-4 aspect-h-3 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500">
              <span>South West Map/Image</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>